[ User ] 
   │
   │ 1. Login/Signup
   ▼
[ Auth Service (auth_app) ]
   │
   │ 2. Returns JWT (token with user's email as `sub`)
   ▼
[ Frontend (Next.js) ]
   │
   │ 3. Stores token (e.g. localStorage)
   │
   │ 4. Upload Video Request (includes token in Authorization header)
   ▼
[ Backend Service (backend) ]
   │
   │ 5. Verifies token using shared secret from .env
   │
   │ 6. Saves video file, passes token + file to Pose Analysis
   ▼
[ Pose Service (pose-service) ]
   │
   │ 7. Verifies token again
   │
   │ 8. Processes pose estimation
   │
   │ 9. Sends result back to backend
   ▼
[ Backend ]
   │
   │ 10. Saves results, responds to frontend
   ▼
[ Frontend Displays Result ]
